<div id="section2">
  
  </div> <table class="sections" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tr>
    <td class="section u5"><!-- block --> 
<div class="block-wrapper odd block_1">
  <div id="block-ddblock-4" class="block block-ddblock themed-block">
        <div class="content"><!-- dynamic display block slideshow -->
<div id="ddblock-4" class="ddblock-cycle-upright10 clear-block">
 <div class="container clear-block border">
  <div class="container-inner clear-block border">
      <!-- slider content -->
   <div class="slider clear-block border">
    <div class="slider-inner clear-block border">
                  <div class="slide clear-block border">
        <div class="slide-inner clear-block border">
         <img src="/sites/default/files/20yearsfreedom_celebration2.png" alt="Celebrating 20 Years of Democracy"/>         <div class="slide-text slide-text-vertical slide-text-right clear-block border">
          <div class="slide-text-inner clear-block border">
           <div class="slide-title slide-title-vertical clear-block border">
            <div class="slide-title-inner clear-block border">
             <h2>Celebrating 20 Years of Democracy</h2>
            </div> <!-- slide-title-inner-->
           </div>  <!-- slide-title-->
           <div class="slide-body-vertical clear-block border">
            <div class="slide-body-inner clear-block border">
             <p><p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	The past 20 years have seen a dramatic and sustained process of formation of environmental guiding principles, institution building and restructuring, legislation and policy development, and domestic and international engagement -&nbsp;all with the intention of addressing the historical legacy of inequality, international isolation and the fragmented structures of environmental governance.</p>
<p class="rteright">
	<strong><a href="https://www.environment.gov.za/20years_ofdemocracy">read more...</a></strong></p>
</p>
            </div> <!-- slide-body-inner-->
           </div>  <!-- slide-body-->
           <div class="slide-read-more slide-read-more-vertical clear-block border">
            <p></p>
	         </div><!-- slide-read-more-->
          </div> <!-- slide-text-inner-->
         </div>  <!-- slide-text-->
        </div> <!-- slide-inner-->
       </div>  <!-- slide-->
             <div class="slide clear-block border">
        <div class="slide-inner clear-block border">
         <img src="/sites/default/files/reipppp_scrollbanner.png" alt="REIPPPP 4th bidding round submission deadline"/>         <div class="slide-text slide-text-vertical slide-text-right clear-block border">
          <div class="slide-text-inner clear-block border">
           <div class="slide-title slide-title-vertical clear-block border">
            <div class="slide-title-inner clear-block border">
             <h2>REIPPPP 4th bidding round submission deadline</h2>
            </div> <!-- slide-title-inner-->
           </div>  <!-- slide-title-->
           <div class="slide-body-vertical clear-block border">
            <div class="slide-body-inner clear-block border">
             <p><p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	The Department of Environmental Affairs (herein referred to as &quot;this Department&quot;) kindly requests Environmental Assessment Practitioners (EAPs) and Applicants to ensure that all reports for decision making (i.e. Final Basic Assessment Reports and Final Environmental impact Assessment Reports) are submitted.&nbsp;Follow the link below to see the submission dates...</p>
<p class="rteright">
	<a href="/sites/default/files/docs/reipppp_submission.pdf"><strong>read more...</strong></a></p>
</p>
            </div> <!-- slide-body-inner-->
           </div>  <!-- slide-body-->
           <div class="slide-read-more slide-read-more-vertical clear-block border">
            <p></p>
	         </div><!-- slide-read-more-->
          </div> <!-- slide-text-inner-->
         </div>  <!-- slide-text-->
        </div> <!-- slide-inner-->
       </div>  <!-- slide-->
             <div class="slide clear-block border">
        <div class="slide-inner clear-block border">
         <img src="/sites/default/files/gudetorhinos_webbanner_0.png" alt="Guide to rhinos"/>         <div class="slide-text slide-text-vertical slide-text-right clear-block border">
          <div class="slide-text-inner clear-block border">
           <div class="slide-title slide-title-vertical clear-block border">
            <div class="slide-title-inner clear-block border">
             <h2>Guide to rhinos</h2>
            </div> <!-- slide-title-inner-->
           </div>  <!-- slide-title-->
           <div class="slide-body-vertical clear-block border">
            <div class="slide-body-inner clear-block border">
             <p><p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	South African government is aggressively implementing new and amended legislation and policies, reviewing existing programmes to ensure they meet the needs of those who fight the war on poaching on the ground, and constantly exploring new alternatives to end this scourge. Details of these initiatives are outlined in the pages of this booklet.</p>
<p class="rteright">
	<a href="/sites/default/files/legislations/guideto_rhino.pdf" target="_blank"><strong>read more...</strong></a></p>
</p>
            </div> <!-- slide-body-inner-->
           </div>  <!-- slide-body-->
           <div class="slide-read-more slide-read-more-vertical clear-block border">
            <p></p>
	         </div><!-- slide-read-more-->
          </div> <!-- slide-text-inner-->
         </div>  <!-- slide-text-->
        </div> <!-- slide-inner-->
       </div>  <!-- slide-->
             <div class="slide clear-block border">
        <div class="slide-inner clear-block border">
         <img src="/sites/default/files/world_wildlife_day.png" alt="World Wildlife Day - 03 March 2014 "/>         <div class="slide-text slide-text-vertical slide-text-right clear-block border">
          <div class="slide-text-inner clear-block border">
           <div class="slide-title slide-title-vertical clear-block border">
            <div class="slide-title-inner clear-block border">
             <h2>World Wildlife Day - 03 March 2014 </h2>
            </div> <!-- slide-title-inner-->
           </div>  <!-- slide-title-->
           <div class="slide-body-vertical clear-block border">
            <div class="slide-body-inner clear-block border">
             <p><p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	On 20 December 2013, at its 68th session, the United Nations General Assembly decided to proclaim 3 March, the day of the adoption the Convention on International Trade in Endangered Species of Wild Fauna and Flora (CITES), as World Wildlife Day. Follow the link below for more information&nbsp;about the event...</p>
<p class="rteright">
	<strong><a href="/event/world_wildlife_day">read more...</a></strong></p>
</p>
            </div> <!-- slide-body-inner-->
           </div>  <!-- slide-body-->
           <div class="slide-read-more slide-read-more-vertical clear-block border">
            <p></p>
	         </div><!-- slide-read-more-->
          </div> <!-- slide-text-inner-->
         </div>  <!-- slide-text-->
        </div> <!-- slide-inner-->
       </div>  <!-- slide-->
               </div> <!-- slider-inner-->
   </div>  <!-- slider-->
       <!-- number pager --> 
     <div class="spacer-horizontal"><b></b></div>
<!-- number pager -->
<div id="ddblock-number-pager-4" class="number-pager ddblock-pager clear-block">
</div> 
<div class="number-pager-pre-bottom "></div>
     </div> <!-- container-inner-->
 </div> <!--container-->
</div> <!--  template -->
</div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- /block --> </td>                </tr>
  </table> <!-- /section2 -->
